  "detailed_description": "Drive Isle is an open world driving game mainly focused on random driving <br />\r\nand drifting, if you will.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n• Semi-realistic driving physics<br />\r\n• Hundreds of kilometers of road to drive<br />\r\n• Gas stations & adjustable fuel consumption<br />\r\n• Adjustable visual & mechanical damage<br />\r\n• Interior (cockpit) view in all vehicles<br />\r\n• 30+ real world resembling vehicles<br />\r\n• Missions and races to earn money<br />\r\n• Option to start new game owning all vehicles and just drive<br />\r\n• Performance and visual upgrades & gadgets such as additional gauges<br />\r\n• Multiple houses with parking slots to purchase<br />\r\n• 2000km² sized map with a winter area up north<br />\r\n• Inventory system (find / sell / store / purchase / use items)",
  "about_the_game": "Drive Isle is an open world driving game mainly focused on random driving <br />\r\nand drifting, if you will.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n• Semi-realistic driving physics<br />\r\n• Hundreds of kilometers of road to drive<br />\r\n• Gas stations & adjustable fuel consumption<br />\r\n• Adjustable visual & mechanical damage<br />\r\n• Interior (cockpit) view in all vehicles<br />\r\n• 30+ real world resembling vehicles<br />\r\n• Missions and races to earn money<br />\r\n• Option to start new game owning all vehicles and just drive<br />\r\n• Performance and visual upgrades & gadgets such as additional gauges<br />\r\n• Multiple houses with parking slots to purchase<br />\r\n• 2000km² sized map with a winter area up north<br />\r\n• Inventory system (find / sell / store / purchase / use items)",
